Question: Do you think standard tests accurately assess student abilities?
Answer:
I grew up with and did well on Standardized tests so I dont really have an opinion on standardized tests. That being said, I think that schools in general need to re-evaluate how they assess students abilities.  I believe that teachets should not gauge a students worth based on their grades alone, especially with struggling students.  Every student is different and has different strengths and weaknesses.  So I guess I do have an opinion on standardized tests.  They do not accurately assess a students abilities.